data.description: Welcome to your renovated haven! Inside, enjoy the contemporary touch of Lvp flooring in key areas and elegant tile in the kitchen and master bathroom. The entire interior has been refreshed with new paint, giving a modern and timeless feel. The guest rooms and bonus area have plush new carpets, ensuring comfort and style. This property boasts a master bathroom retreat with upgraded tile features, including a rebuilt shower wall for added assurance. The enclosed garage attached to the home, is a wonderful additional living space, complete with a bar ready for entertaining. Step into the expansive backyard, a perfect canvas for your outdoor dreams. With a detached garage for parking, storage, or a workshop, your options are limitless. Discover versatility in this home's layout! The fourth bedroom, conveniently situated upstairs, offers flexibility as a bonus room or a versatile flex space. Customize it to suit your needs, whether it's a cozy bedroom retreat, a dynamic entertainment area, or a productive home office. This additional space adds a layer of adaptability to complement your lifestyle. Welcome home to your retreat of comfort and possibilities!
